# Kwazi Lehlohonolo Mashaya - CV Website

This is a responsive and professional **CV website** built using only **HTML and CSS** — no frameworks or JavaScript — as per project requirements for the Dynamic DNA Learnership (2024).

## 🔗 Live Preview

[Visit My Portfolio](https://kwazi-code.github.io/MyWebsite/)  
Or scan the QR code on the website.

## 📄 Project Purpose

The goal of this project was to:
- Create a clean, readable CV using web technologies
- Practice semantic HTML and responsive CSS layouts
- Avoid any JavaScript, frameworks, or libraries
- Build a presentable portfolio to showcase skills and experience

## 🛠️ Built With

- **HTML5**
- **CSS3**

